story: MIT African Students' Association - ASA added an event.
message:
The whole Village(Kijiji) will come live on Monday with a classy photoshoot by our famed photographer.

Wear your African attire for a photoshoot as we drum up the Cultural night vibes. If you don't have any, just come. We will have something for you.

We got ASA Swag discount for all who attend. Yes, you heard that right! ASA hoodies, and Tee's, fresh outta Africa.

We are meeting in lobby 13, but your photo shoot will take place at one of the most beautiful settings of Killian, lobby 7, and the Scenic Charles river.

And you know how we roll... There will be good food, good music, and good people.

Alllll are welcomed! We gonna lay it out! Tell your friends!
